bayonet grass
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Aciphylla</i> spp., an old name for  speargrass or taramea,  contrast <i>A. squarrosa</i> a little later `soft leaved Spear grass',  =spear-grass cf bayonet-plant.
